{"tid":220163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國最大「空心」摩天輪      創3世界之最","createTime":"2017-04-27T18:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T02:32:13.000Z","uid":58099,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63d66788a6dd059e6e395f042008d9412c6aba2e","tid":220163,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170426/large/1493220313_a5df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170426%2Flarge%2F1493220313_a5df.jpg&h=76248cff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界最大「空心」摩天輪即將在中國山東濰坊建成，摩天輪總高度145米，直徑達125米，觀景廂有Wifi、電視等。每個廂可容納10人，每次運轉時間為28分鐘。昨日有多角度航拍片曝光，意味摩天輪開幕在即。<br />\n<br />\n白浪河大橋摩天輪創下了三個世界之最：最大的無軸式摩天輪、首用編織網格形式摩天輪及首次無軸式輪橋合一摩天輪。據工程總承包方中建六局負責人介紹，白浪河大橋摩天輪的輪盤造型的設計靈感來源於中國傳統文化「龍」，整個輪盤如一個首尾相合的「龍脊」。用了兩年時間興建，將重達4,600噸鋼管紡織出巨型鋼鐵「龍脊」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170426/large/1493220314_2e1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170426%2Flarge%2F1493220314_2e1b.jpg&h=ef90bd09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n摩天輪建在白浪河大橋的中央位置，形成世界最高的輪橋合一摩天輪。白浪河大橋全長540米，其中主橋長190米、引橋長350米。主橋為雙層桁架橋，上層為汽車專用道，下層為行人道，也是摩天輪的入口。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170426/large/1493220315_e824.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170426%2Flarge%2F1493220315_e824.jpg&h=85ad6757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n負責人說，要將如此龐然大物置於一座橋上，再加上瀕海巨大的風的荷載，這是巨大的挑戰，「為了保證大橋的承載力，僅樁基就需要打下直徑1米至1.8米、長度48米至76米鑽孔灌注樁404根。為保證摩天輪能夠平衡地坐落在大橋之上，鋼結構空間圓環的斜柱、拉索與輪盤連接處均有環向加強環，以提高摩天輪面外剛度、減少摩天輪在風荷載作用下變形。"},{"pid":"f7b4fafb97c2e28969c60aa98ed5c53827b8d3e1","tid":220163,"uid":72676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:08:02.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7a803f598a621aabe8bf47b735e2d9b2893810","tid":220163,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:10:19.000Z","msg":"百年一遇"},{"pid":"3b0a4563f7db130494513fe4862fb64e89f09d8f","tid":220163,"uid":1991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:11:05.000Z","msg":"最柒 最危險 最九唔搭八"},{"pid":"bbe006b9b59a46a11ba4ba8aee35968387e3a145","tid":220163,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:15:49.000Z","msg":"最偷工減料<br />\n入面係紙皮"},{"pid":"459aba6efedcdba3a4497738007c3eb364ee9fd9","tid":220163,"uid":103212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:48:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08eedcb0ffc373f3135417fa3188332958a7beb7","tid":220163,"uid":13082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:53:16.000Z","msg":"有咩風景睇？"},{"pid":"55f385d093e3ba9c43b42dcaa7a9306762f1f217","tid":220163,"uid":48834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:55:54.000Z","msg":"睇見都驚"},{"pid":"79de31cbb08d98e7f3591d3a35a5db68d09260b5","tid":220163,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:56:41.000Z","msg":"睇相都覺得牙煙"},{"pid":"7c20d2936d0df759342c06045f63d41bc7b44b1a","tid":220163,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:57:49.000Z","msg":"靚係幾靚<br />\n不過命仔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b888a8b10a3b5caffb868385bb8c5672813755d4","tid":220163,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:34:47.000Z","msg":"大霧到咁撚樣，有撚野睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb3c14dca96e8fed76302c40c043b4dc3a1e08d","tid":220163,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T20:01:43.000Z","msg":"點解支那咁鍾意起啲大型圓形建築？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"